Introduction To Nano-Science And Technologies 3 Credits, Pervasive Computing In Vehicular Overlay Network 3 Credits, VLSI Design Automation 3 Credits, VLSI Testing 3 Credits, Logic Synthesis And Verification 3 Credits, etc. (For more courses: http://www.eecs.ntu.edu.tw/interna/super_pages.php?ID=course )
